      • decrementDayForRented

        public void decrementDayForRented()
        Deprecated.
        Decrements the days left in all games that are rented within the list. When I was a young boy, we used to decrement the days by marking an X on the paper calendar. I remember thinking "there must be a better way". Well, here it is.
